@startuml Optimised Sequence Diagram

title Optimised ISRS — Submission and Review Workflow

actor Researcher
boundary UI
control SubmissionController
entity Validator
entity SubmissionRepository
control ReviewAssignmentService
entity ReviewerRepository
entity Reviewer
control EvaluationService
entity ScoreRepository
entity DecisionEngine
boundary NotificationService

== Submission Phase ==

Researcher -> UI : submitResearchOutput(data)
activate UI

UI -> SubmissionController : submit(data)
activate SubmissionController

SubmissionController -> Validator : validateFormat(data)
activate Validator
Validator --> SubmissionController : isValid
deactivate Validator

alt isValid == false
    SubmissionController --> UI : "ERROR: Invalid format"
    UI --> Researcher : error message
else isValid == true

    SubmissionController -> SubmissionRepository : save(data)
    activate SubmissionRepository
    SubmissionRepository --> SubmissionController : submissionId
    deactivate SubmissionRepository

    == Reviewer Assignment Phase ==

    SubmissionController -> ReviewAssignmentService : assignAndCollectScores(submissionId)
    activate ReviewAssignmentService

    ReviewAssignmentService -> ReviewerRepository : findAll()
    activate ReviewerRepository
    ReviewerRepository --> ReviewAssignmentService : candidates
    deactivate ReviewerRepository

    note right of ReviewAssignmentService
        Filter conflicts & workload
        in a single pass
    end note

    loop for each eligible reviewer
        ReviewAssignmentService -> Reviewer : generateScore()
        activate Reviewer
        Reviewer --> ReviewAssignmentService : scoreValue
        deactivate Reviewer
    end

    ReviewAssignmentService --> SubmissionController : List<Score>
    deactivate ReviewAssignmentService

    == Evaluation Phase ==

    SubmissionController -> EvaluationService : evaluate(submissionId, scores)
    activate EvaluationService

    EvaluationService -> ScoreRepository : saveAll(scores)
    activate ScoreRepository
    ScoreRepository --> EvaluationService : done
    deactivate ScoreRepository

    EvaluationService -> DecisionEngine : evaluate(scores)
    activate DecisionEngine

    note right of DecisionEngine
        Decision table logic:
        R2: avg≥7.0 & consensus → ACCEPTED
        R3: avg<5.0 → REJECTED
        R4/R5: else → REVISION_REQUIRED
    end note

    DecisionEngine --> EvaluationService : EvaluationOutcome
    deactivate DecisionEngine

    EvaluationService --> SubmissionController : EvaluationOutcome
    deactivate EvaluationService

    == Notification Phase ==

    SubmissionController -> NotificationService : notify(outcome)
    activate NotificationService
    NotificationService --> SubmissionController : done
    deactivate NotificationService

    SubmissionController --> UI : result
    deactivate SubmissionController
    UI --> Researcher : result
    deactivate UI

end

@enduml
